      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "1998 sedan in good condition. The vehicle is mechanically sound and performs well. There is minor cosmetic wear on the exterior and interior consistent with careful use over time.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
