    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior is immaculate, showing no signs of wear or use. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with every system functioning exactly as intended and a complete service history to back its pristine status. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle of this caliber that has been meticulously preserved by its owner.",
